snippet.title: Evolution Pinball VR: The Summoning trailer
snippet.description:
Experience the thrill of Pinball gaming in Virtual Reality.
Steam Greenlight enabled,Vote Now.

http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=617795618

The Summoning is the first table from Evolution Pinball VR studios specifically built for Virtual reality using full next generation physics and rendering. 
You must summon an entity from another dimension, beware, the entity is not easily controlled and will fight to command you!
